                    <td>3</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td>4</td>
                    <td class="pl">Tyrone Visvakula</td>
                    <td>14</td>
                    <td class="r">527</td>
                    <td>47.91</td>
                    <td>186*</td>
                    <td>2</td>
                    <td>1</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td>5</td>
                    <td class="pl">Daniyal Ahmed</td>
                    <td>14</td>
                    <td class="r">491</td>
                    <td>40.92</td>
                    <td>97</td>
                    <td>3</td>
                    <td>0</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="social-proof">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="proof-label">Trusted by ECB Premier League clubs</div>
        <div class="proof-clubs">
          <div class="proof-club">
            <div class="proof-icon">&#127951;</div>
            <div class="proof-name">Sunbury CC</div>
            <div class="proof-league">Surrey Championship</div>
          </div>
          <div class="proof-club">
            <div class="proof-icon">&#127951;</div>
            <div class="proof-name">Roe Green CC</div>
            <div class="proof-league">Middlesex County League</div>
          </div>
          <div class="proof-club">
            <div class="proof-icon">&#127951;</div>
            <div class="proof-name">Normandy CC</div>
            <div class="proof-league">Surrey Championship</div>
          </div>
          <div class="proof-club">
            <div class="proof-icon">&#127951;</div>
            <div class="proof-name">Old Hamptonians CC</div>
            <div class="proof-league">Middlesex County League</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="demo" class="alt">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-h">
          <div class="eyebrow">Live working demo</div>
          <h2>See a real club dashboard.</h2>
          <p>
            Sunbury CC's senior batting &amp; bowling stats for 2023&ndash;26
            &mdash; built and refreshed by ClubStats. Try the season chips, swap
            teams, sort by strike rate, dig into any XI.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="demo-banner">
          <h2 style="font-size: 26px;">
            Sunbury CC &mdash; Senior, 2023&ndash;26
          </h2>
          <p>
            Click below &mdash; works on desktop or phone. No login required.
          </p>
          <a href="/sunbury" class="btn btn-primary"
            >Open the live dashboard &rarr;</a
          >
        </div>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
          <p style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 14px;">
            Like what you see? Get the same for your club.
          </p>
          <a href="#order" class="btn btn-primary"
            >Order for your club &mdash; &pound;125 &rarr;</
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-h">
          <div class="eyebrow">Why ClubStats</div>
          <h2>
            Your club deserves <span class="h-acc"
              >better than a spreadsheet.</span
            >
          </h2>
          <p>
            Play Cricket has the data, but the experience is built for one
            player at a time, behind a login, on a page nobody opens twice.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="compare">
          <div class="card bad">
            <h3>Play Cricket Statistics</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Requires login for every viewer</li>
              <li>One filter at a time &mdash; no combine</li>
              <li>Looks like it was built in 2008</li>
              <li>Hard to share at AGM or on socials</li>
              <li>No 50s/100s leaderboard, no form table</li>
              <li>Mobile is an afterthought</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card good">
            <h3>Your ClubStats Dashboard</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>One link to share &mdash; no logins</li>
              <li>Multi-season + multi-team combine</li>
              <li>Built to look like Sky Cricket</li>
              <li>Drops into your AGM or WhatsApp</li>
              <li>Leaderboards, top innings, best spells</li>
              <li>Beautiful on phone, tablet &amp; laptop</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features" class="alt">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-h">
          <div class="eyebrow">What's inside</div>
          <h2>Everything you'd want from a Wisden-worthy club dashboard.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-grid">
          <div class="feature navy">
            <div class="icon">&#127951;</div>
            <h3>Batting &amp; Bowling tabs</h3>
            <p>
              Full leaderboards for runs, average, strike rate, 50s, 100s
              &mdash; and on the bowling side, wickets, economy, best figures,
              five-fers.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <div class="icon">&#128197;</div>
            <h3>Multi-season combine</h3>
            <p>
              Click any seasons you want &mdash; 2023 + 2025, or all years
              &mdash; and the numbers correctly recompute. Averages and strike
              rates are properly re-derived.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature green">
            <div class="icon">&#128101;</div>
            <h3>Multi-XI breakdown</h3>
            <p>
              Filter by 1st XI, 2nd XI, or any combination. Per-XI top-5 panels
              for every competition. Selection committees love this view.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <div class="icon">&#11088;</div>
            <h3>Top performance lists</h3>
            <p>
              Standout individual innings and best bowling spells, with the date
              and opposition. Perfect for awards nights and end-of-season
              write-ups.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature navy">
            <div class="icon">&#128200;</div>
            <h3>Year-on-year trend</h3>
            <p>
              Pick 2+ seasons and a per-year trend strip lights up automatically
              &mdash; see who's getting better, who's tailing off, who's the new
              find.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <div class="icon">&#128241;</div>
            <h3>Beautiful on every device</h3>
            <p>
              Loads instantly on a phone in the pavilion, looks the part on a
              big screen at the AGM, opens for anyone you send the link to.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonials">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-h">
          <div class="eyebrow">What clubs say</div>
          <h2>Don't take our word for it.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-grid">
          <div class="testimonial">
            <div class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
            <p class="quote">
              &ldquo;We shared the link in our WhatsApp group and the lads were
              all over it within minutes. The selection committee actually uses
              it now &mdash; that's never happened with Play Cricket.&rdquo;
            </p>
            <div class="author">
              <div class="name">Club Captain</div>
              <div class="club">Sunbury CC</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial">
            <div class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
            <p class="quote">
              &ldquo;Brilliant for the AGM. We just pulled it up on the
              projector and went through the stats team by team. Looked
              professional and the members loved it.&rdquo;
            </p>
            <div class="author">
              <div class="name">Club Chairman</div>
              <div class="club">Old Hamptonians CC</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial">
            <div class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
            <p class="quote">
              &ldquo;Setup took no effort on our side. Sent them the Play
              Cricket link on Monday, had a working dashboard by Wednesday.
              Updates itself every week &mdash; couldn't be easier.&rdquo;
            </p>
            <div class="author">
              <div class="name">Fixtures Secretary</div>
              <div class="club">Normandy CC</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;">
          <a href="#order" class="btn btn-primary"
            >Get this for your club &rarr;</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="how">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-h">
          <div class="eyebrow">How it works</div>
          <h2>Live in 48 hours. No tech required.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="how-grid">
          <div class="how-step">
            <div class="num">1</div>
            <h4>Order</h4>
            <p>
              Order below for &pound;125. Tell us your club's Play Cricket
              address and which XIs to include.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="how-step">
            <div class="num">2</div>
            <h4>We do the work</h4>
            <p>
              Within 48 hours we pull every senior stat from the last four
              seasons, in your club colours.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="how-step">
            <div class="num">3</div>
            <h4>Get your URL</h4>
            <p>
              You receive <strong>clubcricketstats.com/yourclub</strong> &mdash; share with
              the committee, players, and your members.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="how-step">
            <div class="num">4</div>
            <h4>Weekly refresh</h4>
            <p>
              Every Sunday night during the season, we re-capture and update.
              The URL never changes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="pricing" class="alt">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-h">
          <div class="eyebrow">Pricing</div>
          <h2>One price. <span class="h-acc">No surprises.</span></h2>
          <p>
            Cheaper than a new set of bails for the third team, more useful than
            half the kit in the changing room.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-wrap">
          <div class="pricing-card">
            <div class="banner">&#127881; Launch offer &mdash; first 20 clubs only</div>
            <div class="body">
              <div class="price-slashed">
                <span class="was">&pound;199</span>
              </div>
              <div class="price">
                <span class="cur">&pound;</span>125
              </div>
              <div class="pre">Setup + first year &mdash; save &pound;74</div>
              <div class="recur">Just &pound;99.99/year after</div>
              <ul>
                <li>Full setup in 48 hours</li>
                <li>Last 4 seasons of stats included</li>
                <li>Batting + Bowling dashboards</li>
                <li>Multi-season &amp; multi-XI combine</li>
                <li>Weekly auto-refresh during season</li>
                <li>Your club crest &amp; colours</li>
                <li>Permanent URL (clubcricketstats.com/yourclub)</li>
                <li>End-of-season PDF for the AGM</li>
                <li>Email support all year</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="#order" class="btn btn-primary">Order for your club</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="order">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-h">
          <div class="eyebrow">Order in 60 seconds</div>
          <h2>Get your dashboard live by the weekend.</h2>
          <p>
            Fill in the form &mdash; we'll be in touch within an hour to confirm
            and arrange Play Cricket access.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="order-wrap">
          <h3>Your club's dashboard</h3>
          <p class="intro">
            No payment taken yet &mdash; we confirm details first, then send a
            Stripe link.
          </p>
          <form
            action="mailto:hello@clubcricketstats.com"
            method="post"
            enctype="text/plain"
          >
            <div class="form-row two">
              <div>
                <label for="clubname">Club name</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="clubname"
                  name="clubname"
                  placeholder="e.g. Sunbury CC"
                  required
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="subdomain">Play Cricket subdomain</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="subdomain"
                  name="subdomain"
                  placeholder="the bit before .play-cricket.com"
                  required
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row two">
              <div>
                <label for="contact">Your name</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="contact"
                  name="contact"
                  placeholder="Jane Captain"
                  required
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="role">Your role at the club</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="role"
                  name="role"
                  placeholder="e.g. Chair of Selection"
                  required
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row two">
              <div>
                <label for="email">Email</label>
                <input
                  type="email"
                  id="email"
                  name="email"
                  placeholder="jane@yourclub.co.uk"
                  required
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="phone">Phone (optional)</label>
                <input
                  type="tel"
                  id="phone"
                  name="phone"
                  placeholder="+44 ..."
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row two">
              <div>
                <label for="teams">Teams to include</label>
                <select id="teams" name="teams">
                  <option>1st XI only</option>
                  <option>1st &amp; 2nd XI</option>
                  <option>1st, 2nd, 3rd XI</option>
                  <option selected>All senior XIs we have</option>
                  <option>Senior + junior sections (extra &pound;49)</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="colours">Club colours</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="colours"
                  name="colours"
                  placeholder="e.g. Navy & gold"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row">
              <label for="notes">Anything else we should know?</label>
              <textarea
                id="notes"
                name="notes"
                placeholder="Optional — anything specific you want highlighted, deadlines, etc."
              ></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="total">
              <div>
                <div class="lbl">Today's order</div>
                <strong>Setup + first year</strong>
              </div>
              <div class="amt"><span class="was-sm">&pound;199</span> &pound;125</div>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary"
              >Submit order &rarr;</button
            >
            <p class="fine">
              By submitting, you agree to our terms. We'll be in touch within
              one hour during UK business hours. &pound;99.99 annual renewal
              each season &mdash; cancel anytime, no questions asked. Launch
              price available for the first 20 clubs only.
            </p>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="faq" class="alt">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-h">
          <div class="eyebrow">FAQ</div>
          <h2>Things clubs ask before they order.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <details class="faq" open>
            <summary>Do you need our Play Cricket login?</summary>
            <p>
              Yes &mdash; briefly. The full stats page on Play Cricket sits
              behind sign-in, so we need access to capture your numbers. We'll
              arrange this securely on a quick screen-share (10 minutes), or you
              can paste a one-time login into a password manager link we send
              you. We don't store credentials.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary>How current are the stats?</summary>
            <p>
              On setup we pull every match from the last four seasons. During
              the season, we re-capture every Sunday night so Monday morning
              your URL is fresh.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary>Can I include the junior section too?</summary>
            <p>
              Yes &mdash; Under-9 through Under-18 cricket can be added as a
              bolt-on for &pound;49. We add a separate "Junior" mode to the
              dashboard so seniors and juniors stay clearly separated.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary>Who can see the URL?</summary>
            <p>
              Anyone you share it with &mdash; no login. Treat it like an
              unlisted YouTube video: not advertised, not indexed by Google, but
              viewable by anyone with the URL. If you'd rather have password
              protection, we offer that as a &pound;30 add-on.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary>What's included in the &pound;99/year renewal?</summary>
            <p>
              Weekly stats refresh through every season, all new feature
              releases (we ship most weeks), continued hosting, and email
              support. If a season ends and you don't want to renew, the
              dashboard stops updating but stays live for the rest of the
              calendar year as a free archive.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary>What about T20s, midweek leagues, friendlies?</summary>
            <p>
              All competitions Play Cricket records show up &mdash; we let you
